OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FRuling could transform rape
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fcases in Scottish courts   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A landmark ruling by senior judges     
OL,6, could transform how rape cases are     
OL,7, prosecuted in Scotland, the country's  
OL,8, top law officer has said.              
OL,10,FThe panel of seven Appeal Court judges 
OL,11,Fsaid that there will no longer need to 
OL,12,Fbe evidence from two separate sources  
OL,13,Fthat penetration has taken place.      
OL,15,FInstead, evidence that the victim was  
OL,16,Fdistressed afterwards could be used to 
OL,17,Fcorroborate the rape allegation.       
OL,19,FThe court had been asked to examine the
OL,20,Fissue by Lord Advocate Dorothy Bain KC.
